  "prompt": "Which is the best coaching in Patna for the IIT-JEE?",
  "response": "Patna has several coaching institutes that are well-regarded for IIT-JEE preparation. Some of the prominent ones include:\n\n1. **FIITJEE Patna**: Known for its experienced faculty and comprehensive study material.\n2. **Resonance**: Offers rigorous training and consistent test series.\n3. **Aakash Institute**: Renowned for its structured courses and effective teaching methods.\n4. **Mentors Eduserv**: A popular choice with a good track record for IIT-JEE results.\n5. **Vision Classes**: Provides personalized attention and quality education.\n\nIt's important to choose a coaching institute based on factors like faculty experience, success rates, student reviews, and your individual learning needs. Visiting each institute, attending demo classes, and speaking with current students can also help in making an informed decision.",
